reviewText: My twin girls are die hard "BobBob" fans. They have enjoyed this DVD very much. They especially love the "Cowboy Bob" episode. It's nice to watch Spongebob with no commercials, but I don't think it is as creative or as original as it used to be, but as long as my kids enjoy it, I will purchase all things Bob Bob.
Title: SpongeBob SquarePants - Pest of the West
